data.description: Welcome to this exquisite 5-bedroom, 3.5-bathroom residence spanning a generous 2,869 square feet of open living space. Nestled in a gated community offering added privacy and security. Beautiful two-story home built in 2014, but shows like a new build. This home has a low maintenance front yard. The backyard is ready for you to enjoy tranquil nights and host Weekend BBQs. Located close to Parks, shopping & restaurants!
